;††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††Ы;Ы;ALLOCATE.ACT - dynamic runtime memoryЫ;allocation routinesЫ;Ы;Copyright (c) 1984 OSS,Inc. and Mark RoseЫ;Ы;   User should declare a CARD variableЫ;   called "EndProg" at the beginningЫ;   of his program and then includeЫ;   this file immediately after.Ы;   The following SET should beЫ;   performed after compiling theЫ;   program but before running it:Ы;      >SET EndProg=*Ы;   The user should call AllocInitЫ;   to set up a new free list afterЫ;   getting into highest graphicsЫ;   mode required.Ы;††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††††ЫЫMODULEЫЫDEFINE NULL="0"ЫЫTYPE BLOCK=[CARD size,next]ЫЫCARD MemLo=$2E7, MemHi=$2E5ЫЫBLOCK POINTER FreeListЫЫ;************************************Ы;Allocate nBytes and return addressЫ;of blockЫ;************************************ЫЫCARD FUNC Alloc(CARD nBytes)ЫЫ  BLOCK POINTER last, current,Ы                targetЫЫ  last=FreeList ; start at beginning of listЫ  current=FreeList.nextЫЫ  ;search list for a block of sufficient sizeЫ  WHILE (current<>NULL) AND (current.size<nBytes)Ы    DOЫ    last=currentЫ    current=current.nextЫ    ODЫЫ  IF current=NULL THENЫ    RETURN(NULL) ;couldn't find a blockЫ  FIЫЫ  ;first case - block is exactly the right sizeЫ  IF current.size=nBytes THENЫ    last.next=current.next ; just remove this blockЫ    target=current         ; from the free listЫ    RETURN(target)Ы   FIЫЫ  ;second case - block is bigger than requestedЫ  current.size==-nBytes ; remove from countЫ  target=current+current.size ;allocate from right endЫ  target.size=nBytesЫRETURN(target)ЫЫ;************************************Ы;Free a block and add it to the freeЫ;listЫ;************************************ЫЫPROC Free(BLOCK POINTER target  CARD nBYTES)ЫЫ  BLOCK POINTER last, currentЫЫ  target.size=nBytesЫ  last=FreeListЫ  current=FreeList.nextЫЫ  ;search for position to put freed blockЫ  WHILE (current<>NULL) AND (current<target)Ы    DOЫ    last=currentЫ    current=current.nextЫ    ODЫЫ  ;found spot, now add block to free listЫ  IF last+last.size=target THENЫ    last.size==+nBytesЫ  ELSEЫ    target.next=currentЫ    last.next=targetЫ  FIЫЫ  ;now check for right side adjacencyЫ  IF target+nBytes=current THENЫ    target.size==+current.sizeЫ    target.next=current.nextЫ  FIЫRETURNЫЫ;************************************Ы;set up the free listЫ;************************************ЫЫPROC AllocInit(CARD useless)ЫЫ  BLOCK POINTER pЫЫ  p=EndProgЫ  FreeList.next=PЫ  p.next=NULLЫ  p.size=MemHi-PЫRETURNЫЫ;************************************Ы;print out the free listЫ;************************************ЫЫPROC PrintFreeList()ЫЫ  BLOCK POINTER pЫЫ  P=FreeList.nextЫ  WHILE p<>NULLЫ    DOЫ    PrintF("%H: %H  %H%E",p,p.size,p.next)Ы    p=p.nextЫ    ODЫRETURNЫЫ;†≈од†пж†Ѕћћѕ√ЃЅ√‘†ЫЫMODULEЫЫ